## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current statistics or emerging trends in poverty. Additionally, the complexity of poverty means that not all contributing factors can be fully explored in this brief report. Further research is recommended to explore regional variations and the impact of recent global events on poverty.